 upon him, in his dream on the night he was killed the following morning. The Prophet said, \u201cO Uthman, break your fast with us tonight.\" Then, he was killed while he was fasting. Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27047,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/20\/most-haya-uthman\/","url_meta":{"origin":6538,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Uthman: Most modest of the Ummah is Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith, and the most modest of my nation is Uthman.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq li-Ibn 'Asa\u0304kir 39\/92 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35715,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/20\/uthman-bored-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":6538,"position":2},"title":"Uthman on Quran: If we were pure, never bored of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sufyan reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf our hearts were pure, we would never be tired of the speech of Allah.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 7\/272 \u0639\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0648\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0637\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0634\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0639\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 7\/272 \u062d\u0644\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0644\u064a\u0627\u0621 \u0644\u0623\u0628\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36955,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/19\/uthman-slave-ear\/","url_meta":{"origin":6538,"position":3},"title":"Uthman on Qisas: The Caliph lets his servant take retribution on himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Malih reported: Uthman ibn Affan, may Allah be pleased with him, entered his house to find his servant boy playing in the trough of a camel. Uthman took him by the ear and twisted it, but he later regretted what he did. He said to him, \u201cTake my ear\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&qu